  "description": "Add Navigation Link from Homepage Button to Contact Page\n\nCreate a clickable button labeled \"Skontaktuj się\" (Contact Us in Polish) on the homepage that navigates users to the contact subpage when clicked.\n\nRequirements:\n- Place the \"Skontaktuj się\" button in an appropriate location on the homepage (header, hero section, or footer)\n- Configure the button to route to the contact page URL when clicked\n- Ensure the button styling matches the existing design system\n- Verify the link works correctly (no 404 errors, correct page loads)\n- Make the button keyboard accessible (can be activated via Enter/Space)\n- Add appropriate hover and focus states for better UX\n- Test that the navigation works on both desktop and mobile viewports\n- Ensure the contact page exists and is ready to receive traffic",
